trans-unit.source: Provides listener-channel notifications from protocol handlers to the worker process framework.
trans-unit.target: Gir lytterkanal varslinger fra protokollbehandlere i arbeidsprosessen prosessen rammeverket.

trans-unit.source: Also enables protocol handlers to access additional parameters, such as the ID of the listener channel.
trans-unit.target: Gjør det også mulig protokollbehandlere tilgang tilleggsparametere, for eksempel IDen for lytterkanal.

trans-unit.source: IListenerChannelCallback is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: IListenerChannelCallback introduseres i den [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se [versjoner og oppdatering av avhengigheter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Retrieves data that the protocol manager will pass to a listener channel when the protocol manager is starting that listener channel.
trans-unit.target: Henter data transportbehandling for protokollen skal sendes til en lytterkanal når protokollen manager starter den lytterkanal.
